%vlocity_namespace%__Element__c.Name: zen-preamble
%vlocity_namespace%__Element__c.%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c:
{"controlWidth":12,"label":"TextBlock1","text":"

The Road to Enlightenment

Littering a dark and dreary road lay the past relics of complex brand governance, broken CSS support, and abandoned browsers and devices.

We must clear the mind of the past. Targeted micro-segment branding and governance has been achieved thanks to the tireless efforts of the OmniStudio development team.

The OS Zen Garden invites you to relax and meditate on the important lessons of the masters. Begin to see with clarity. Learn to use the time-honored techniques in new and invigorating fashion. Become one with the OmniScript.

","show":null,"dataJSON":false,"HTMLTemplateId":"","textKey":"","sanitize":false}

%vlocity_namespace%__Element__c.Name: zen-explanation
%vlocity_namespace%__Element__c.%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c:
{"controlWidth":12,"label":"TextBlock1","text":"

So What is This About?

\n

There is a continuing need to show the power of CSS. The OmniScript Zen Garden aims to excite, inspire, and encourage custom design in an OmniScript. To begin, view some of the existing designs in the list. Clicking on any one will load the style sheet into this very page. The OmniScript remains the same, the only thing that has changed is the CSS file in Static Resources. Yes, really.

\n

CSS allows complete and total control over the style of a hypertext document. The only way this can be illustrated in a way that gets people excited is by demonstrating what it can truly be, once the reins are placed in the hands of those able to create beauty from structure. Designers and coders alike have contributed to the beauty of the web; we can always push it further.

","show":null,"dataJSON":false,"HTMLTemplateId":"","textKey":"","sanitize":false}

%vlocity_namespace%__Element__c.Name: zen-benefits
%vlocity_namespace%__Element__c.%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c:
{"controlWidth":12,"label":"TextBlock1","text":"

Benefits

\n

Why participate? For recognition, inspiration, and a resource we can all refer to showing people how amazing CSS really can be inside an OmniScript. This site serves as equal parts inspiration for those working on the web today, learning tool for those who will be tomorrow, and gallery of future techniques we can all look forward to.

","show":null,"dataJSON":false,"HTMLTemplateId":"","textKey":"","sanitize":false}

%vlocity_namespace%__Element__c.Name: zen-participation
%vlocity_namespace%__Element__c.%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c:
{"controlWidth":12,"label":"TextBlock1","text":"

Participation

\n

Strong visual design should always be in focus. You may modify the style sheet in any way you wish, but do not change the OmniScript. This may seem daunting at first if you’ve never worked this way before, but purpose is to build your confidence that an OmniScript can be adapted to any design our customers desire.
